 general model and discuss some ramifications for\nmodelling pertinent two- and three-phase flow problems in igneous systems.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 31 Aug 2018 23:00:26 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 26 Apr 2019 21:33:20 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sat, 15 Jun 2019 00:15:56 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-07-05"}
